            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In the summary provided by ARIE, it seems that <foreign>cīruraittār</foreign> has been attributed to Māṇikkavācakar. However, there is no textual nor epigraphical evidence that this was an epithet of the saint. Moreover, it seems more in line with the original that <foreign>uraittār</foreign> is taken simply as reciter(s) of the glory <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>cīr</foreign></supplied> of the three saints <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>mūṉṟukkum</foreign></supplied>.</p>
            </div>
            
